1. *Eksplozija* je čula u daljini. (An *explosion* was heard in the distance.)
2. Policija je pronašla dokaze koji ukazuju na *eksploziju*. (The police found evidence indicating an *explosion*.)
3. U proizvodnoj hali je došlo do *eksplozije*. (There was an *explosion* in the production hall.)
4. *Eksploziju* su uzrokovali neispravni električni uređaji. (*Explosion* was caused by faulty electrical equipment.)
5. Nakon *eksplozije*, vatrogasci su brzo reagovali i uspjeli da ugase požar. (After the *explosion*, firefighters quickly responded and managed to put out the fire.)
6. Neki ljudi osjećaju strah kada čuju zvuk *eksplozije*. (Some people feel fear when they hear the sound of an *explosion*.)
7. Pucanj u zrak zvuči kao *eksplozija*. (A gunshot sounds like an *explosion*.)
8. Dizajneri su se inspirisali *eksplozijom* boja u prirodi. (Designers were inspired by an *explosion* of colors in nature.)
9. Uzbuđenje je bilo poput *eksplozije* u mom tijelu. (Excitement was like an *explosion* in my body.)
10. Sportisti koriste *eksplozivnu* snagu u kratkim trkama. (Athletes use *explosive* power in short sprints.)